comments.body: The security group record should have been deleted after the group is deleted and the issue was fixed in EUCA-11278. In 4.1.2., the record should be deleted from the database manually.

Thanks. Please let me know how one has to delete the security group
manually in 4.1.2 , because it can't be seen in the list of security groups
and a delete command does nothing in the backend. Shall I go inside the
database and run the SQL manually ?

Cheers,
Deependra

On Fri, Sep 11, 2015 at 3:05 AM, Dmitrii Zagorodnov (JIRA) <
[~dshekhawat] You need to delete the affected group from eucalyptus_loadbalancing.metadata_group. I believe the security group was deleted from EC2 but the record remains with ELB.
